author: desruisseaux
msg: Removed the "(derived from geotk-##") part in the "@since 0.#" javadoc annotation.
I think it is not in ASF usages to carry such links to an history outside Apache,
and removing them will also allow us to enable the "since" tags in the generated javadoc
without distracting the users with an information not relevant to the Apache SIS project.
